{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":25,"text":"Okay, now I don't want\nto alarm anybody in this room,"},{"time":5000,"text":"but it's just come to my attention\nthat the person to your right is a liar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":11000,"text":"Also, the person to your left is a liar."},{"time":14000,"text":"Also the person sitting\nin your very seats is a liar."},{"time":17000,"text":"We're all liars."},{"time":19000,"text":"What I'm going to do today"},{"time":21000,"text":"is I'm going to show you what the research\nsays about why we're all liars,"},{"time":24600,"text":"how you can become a liespotter"},{"time":26200,"text":"and why you might want\nto go the extra mile"},{"time":29000,"text":"and go from liespotting to truth seeking,"},{"time":32000,"text":"and ultimately to trust building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34000,"text":"Now, speaking of trust,"},{"time":37000,"text":"ever since I wrote\nthis book, \"Liespotting,\""},{"time":40000,"text":"no one wants to meet me in person\nanymore, no, no, no, no, no."},{"time":43000,"text":"They say, \"It's okay, we'll email you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"I can't even get\na coffee date at Starbucks."},{"time":52000,"text":"My husband's like, \"Honey, deception?"},{"time":54000,"text":"Maybe you could have focused on cooking.\nHow about French cooking?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":57215,"text":"So before I get started,\nwhat I'm going to do"},{"time":59382,"text":"is I'm going to clarify my goal for you,"},{"time":62000,"text":"which is not to teach a game of Gotcha."},{"time":64000,"text":"Liespotters aren't those nitpicky kids,"},{"time":66000,"text":"those kids in the back of the room\nthat are shouting, \"Gotcha! Gotcha!"},{"time":69358,"text":"Your eyebrow twitched.\nYou flared your nostril."},{"time":72000,"text":"I watch that TV show 'Lie To Me.'\nI know you're lying.\""},{"time":75000,"text":"No, liespotters are armed"},{"time":77000,"text":"with scientific knowledge\nof how to spot deception."},{"time":80000,"text":"They use it to get to the truth,"},{"time":82000,"text":"and they do what mature\nleaders do everyday;"},{"time":84120,"text":"they have difficult conversations\nwith difficult people,"},{"time":87000,"text":"sometimes during very difficult times."},{"time":89000,"text":"And they start up that path\nby accepting a core proposition,"},{"time":93000,"text":"and that proposition is the following:"},{"time":95000,"text":"Lying is a cooperative act."},{"time":98777,"text":"Think about it, a lie has no power\nwhatsoever by its mere utterance."},{"time":102000,"text":"Its power emerges"},{"time":104000,"text":"when someone else agrees\nto believe the lie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106120,"text":"So I know it may sound like tough love,"},{"time":108120,"text":"but look, if at some point\nyou got lied to,"},{"time":112000,"text":"it's because you agreed to get lied to."},{"time":114000,"text":"Truth number one about lying:\nLying's a cooperative act."},{"time":117000,"text":"Now not all lies are harmful."},{"time":119000,"text":"Sometimes we're willing\nparticipants in deception"},{"time":122000,"text":"for the sake of social dignity,"},{"time":125000,"text":"maybe to keep a secret that should\nbe kept secret, secret."},{"time":128000,"text":"We say, \"Nice song.\""},{"time":130000,"text":"\"Honey, you don't look fat in that, no.\""},{"time":133000,"text":"Or we say, favorite of the digiratti,"},{"time":135000,"text":"\"You know, I just fished\nthat email out of my Spam folder."},{"time":138000,"text":"So sorry.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":141000,"text":"But there are times when we are unwilling\nparticipants in deception."},{"time":144263,"text":"And that can have dramatic costs for us."},{"time":147000,"text":"Last year saw 997 billion dollars"},{"time":150000,"text":"in corporate fraud alone\nin the United States."},{"time":154333,"text":"That's an eyelash\nunder a trillion dollars."},{"time":156372,"text":"That's seven percent of revenues."},{"time":158000,"text":"Deception can cost billions."},{"time":160000,"text":"Think Enron, Madoff, the mortgage crisis."},{"time":163000,"text":"Or in the case\nof double agents and traitors,"},{"time":166000,"text":"like Robert Hanssen or Aldrich Ames,"},{"time":168000,"text":"lies can betray our country,"},{"time":170000,"text":"they can compromise our security,\nthey can undermine democracy,"},{"time":173024,"text":"they can cause the deaths\nof those that defend us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176000,"text":"Deception is actually serious business."},{"time":179000,"text":"This con man, Henry Oberlander,\nhe was such an effective con man,"},{"time":183000,"text":"British authorities say"},{"time":185000,"text":"he could have undermined the entire\nbanking system of the Western world."},{"time":188500,"text":"And you can't find this guy on Google;\nyou can't find him anywhere."},{"time":191700,"text":"He was interviewed once,\nand he said the following."},{"time":194200,"text":"He said, \"Look, I've got one rule.\""},{"time":195900,"text":"And this was Henry's rule, he said,"},{"time":198000,"text":"\"Look, everyone is willing\nto give you something."},{"time":200400,"text":"They're ready to give you something\nfor whatever it is they're hungry for.\""},{"time":203996,"text":"And that's the crux of it."},{"time":205400,"text":"If you don't want to be\ndeceived, you have to know,"},{"time":207853,"text":"what is it that you're hungry for?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":209553,"text":"And we all kind of hate to admit it."},{"time":212000,"text":"We wish we were\nbetter husbands, better wives,"},{"time":215000,"text":"smarter, more powerful, taller, richer --"},{"time":219000,"text":"the list goes on."},{"time":221000,"text":"Lying is an attempt to bridge that gap,"},{"time":223000,"text":"to connect our wishes and our fantasies"},{"time":225000,"text":"about who we wish we were,\nhow we wish we could be,"},{"time":228000,"text":"with what we're really like."},{"time":231000,"text":"And boy are we willing to fill in\nthose gaps in our lives with lies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234263,"text":"On a given day, studies show\nthat you may be lied to"},{"time":237000,"text":"anywhere from 10 to 200 times."},{"time":239000,"text":"Now granted, many of those are white lies."},{"time":242000,"text":"But in another study,"},{"time":244000,"text":"it showed that strangers lied three times"},{"time":246000,"text":"within the first 10 minutes\nof meeting each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248405,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":250000,"text":"Now when we first hear\nthis data, we recoil."},{"time":253000,"text":"We can't believe how prevalent lying is."},{"time":255000,"text":"We're essentially against lying."},{"time":257000,"text":"But if you look more closely,\nthe plot actually thickens."},{"time":261000,"text":"We lie more to strangers\nthan we lie to coworkers."},{"time":264000,"text":"Extroverts lie more than introverts."},{"time":268000,"text":"Men lie eight times more about themselves\nthan they do other people."},{"time":273000,"text":"Women lie more to protect other people."},{"time":276000,"text":"If you're an average married couple,"},{"time":279000,"text":"you're going to lie to your spouse\nin one out of every 10 interactions."},{"time":283000,"text":"Now, you may think that's bad."},{"time":285000,"text":"If you're unmarried,\nthat number drops to three."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287310,"text":"Lying's complex."},{"time":289000,"text":"It's woven into the fabric\nof our daily and our business lives."},{"time":292024,"text":"We're deeply ambivalent about the truth."},{"time":294000,"text":"We parse it out on an as-needed basis,"},{"time":296000,"text":"sometimes for very good reasons,"},{"time":298000,"text":"other times just because\nwe don't understand the gaps in our lives."},{"time":301215,"text":"That's truth number two about lying."},{"time":303000,"text":"We're against lying,"},{"time":305000,"text":"but we're covertly for it"},{"time":307000,"text":"in ways that our society has sanctioned\nfor centuries and centuries and centuries."},{"time":311024,"text":"It's as old as breathing."},{"time":313000,"text":"It's part of our culture,\nit's part of our history."},{"time":315453,"text":"Think Dante, Shakespeare,\nthe Bible, News of the World."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"Lying has evolutionary value\nto us as a species."},{"time":325310,"text":"Researchers have long known\nthat the more intelligent the species,"},{"time":329000,"text":"the larger the neocortex,"},{"time":331000,"text":"the more likely it is to be deceptive."},{"time":333000,"text":"Now you might remember Koko."},{"time":335000,"text":"Does anybody remember Koko the gorilla\nwho was taught sign language?"},{"time":338263,"text":"Koko was taught to communicate\nvia sign language."},{"time":341000,"text":"Here's Koko with her kitten."},{"time":343000,"text":"It's her cute little, fluffy pet kitten."},{"time":346000,"text":"Koko once blamed her pet kitten\nfor ripping a sink out of the wall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352000,"text":"We're hardwired to become\nleaders of the pack."},{"time":354215,"text":"It's starts really, really early."},{"time":356000,"text":"How early?"},{"time":358000,"text":"Well babies will fake a cry,"},{"time":360000,"text":"pause, wait to see who's coming"},{"time":362000,"text":"and then go right back to crying."},{"time":364000,"text":"One-year-olds learn concealment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":368000,"text":"Two-year-olds bluff."},{"time":370000,"text":"Five-year-olds lie outright."},{"time":372000,"text":"They manipulate via flattery."},{"time":374000,"text":"Nine-year-olds, masters of the cover-up."},{"time":377000,"text":"By the time you enter college,"},{"time":379000,"text":"you're going to lie to your mom\nin one out of every five interactions."},{"time":382400,"text":"By the time we enter this work world\nand we're breadwinners,"},{"time":385300,"text":"we enter a world that is just cluttered\nwith Spam, fake digital friends,"},{"time":389000,"text":"partisan media,"},{"time":391000,"text":"ingenious identity thieves,"},{"time":393000,"text":"world-class Ponzi schemers,"},{"time":395000,"text":"a deception epidemic --"},{"time":397000,"text":"in short, what one author calls\na post-truth society."},{"time":402001,"text":"It's been very confusing\nfor a long time now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408665,"text":"What do you do?"},{"time":410000,"text":"Well, there are steps we can take\nto navigate our way through the morass."},{"time":414000,"text":"Trained liespotters get to the truth\n90 percent of the time."},{"time":417000,"text":"The rest of us,\nwe're only 54 percent accurate."},{"time":420000,"text":"Why is it so easy to learn?"},{"time":422000,"text":"There are good liars and bad liars."},{"time":424239,"text":"There are no real original liars."},{"time":425900,"text":"We all make the same mistakes.\nWe all use the same techniques."},{"time":428900,"text":"So what I'm going to do is I'm going\nto show you two patterns of deception."},{"time":432553,"text":"And then we're going\nto look at the hot spots"},{"time":434776,"text":"and see if we can find them ourselves."},{"time":436653,"text":"We're going to start with speech."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438300,"text":"(Video) Bill Clinton:\nI want you to listen to me."},{"time":440658,"text":"I'm going to say this again."},{"time":442100,"text":"I did not have sexual relations\nwith that woman, Miss Lewinsky."},{"time":449000,"text":"I never told anybody to lie,\nnot a single time, never."},{"time":453000,"text":"And these allegations are false."},{"time":456000,"text":"And I need to go back to work\nfor the American people."},{"time":458596,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":460596,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":463000,"text":"Pamela Meyer: Okay,\nwhat were the telltale signs?"},{"time":466000,"text":"Well first we heard what's known\nas a non-contracted denial."},{"time":470000,"text":"Studies show that people\nwho are overdetermined in their denial"},{"time":473024,"text":"will resort to formal rather\nthan informal language."},{"time":476000,"text":"We also heard\ndistancing language: \"that woman.\""},{"time":479000,"text":"We know that liars will unconsciously\ndistance themselves"},{"time":481739,"text":"from their subject,"},{"time":483000,"text":"using language as their tool."},{"time":486000,"text":"Now if Bill Clinton had said,\n\"Well, to tell you the truth ...\""},{"time":489072,"text":"or Richard Nixon's favorite,\n\"In all candor ...\""},{"time":491387,"text":"he would have been a dead giveaway"},{"time":493100,"text":"for any liespotter that knows"},{"time":495000,"text":"that qualifying language, as it's called,\nqualifying language like that,"},{"time":498453,"text":"further discredits the subject."},{"time":500000,"text":"Now if he had repeated\nthe question in its entirety,"},{"time":503000,"text":"or if he had peppered his account\nwith a little too much detail --"},{"time":507000,"text":"and we're all really glad\nhe didn't do that --"},{"time":509215,"text":"he would have further discredited himself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":511239,"text":"Freud had it right."},{"time":513000,"text":"Freud said, look,\nthere's much more to it than speech:"},{"time":516000,"text":"\"No mortal can keep a secret."},{"time":519000,"text":"If his lips are silent,\nhe chatters with his fingertips.\""},{"time":522000,"text":"And we all do it no matter\nhow powerful you are."},{"time":525000,"text":"We all chatter with our fingertips."},{"time":527000,"text":"I'm going to show you\nDominique Strauss-Kahn with Obama"},{"time":530000,"text":"who's chattering with his fingertips."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":536000,"text":"Now this brings us to our next pattern,\nwhich is body language."},{"time":542000,"text":"With body language,\nhere's what you've got to do."},{"time":545000,"text":"You've really got to just throw\nyour assumptions out the door."},{"time":548000,"text":"Let the science temper\nyour knowledge a little bit."},{"time":550453,"text":"Because we think liars\nfidget all the time."},{"time":553000,"text":"Well guess what, they're known to freeze\ntheir upper bodies when they're lying."},{"time":556786,"text":"We think liars won't look you in the eyes."},{"time":559000,"text":"Well guess what, they look\nyou in the eyes a little too much"},{"time":561900,"text":"just to compensate for that myth."},{"time":563500,"text":"We think warmth and smiles\nconvey honesty, sincerity."},{"time":567000,"text":"But a trained liespotter\ncan spot a fake smile a mile away."},{"time":571000,"text":"Can you all spot the fake smile here?"},{"time":575000,"text":"You can consciously contract\nthe muscles in your cheeks."},{"time":580000,"text":"But the real smile's in the eyes,\nthe crow's feet of the eyes."},{"time":583000,"text":"They cannot be consciously contracted,"},{"time":585000,"text":"especially if you overdid the Botox."},{"time":587000,"text":"Don't overdo the Botox;\nnobody will think you're honest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590000,"text":"Now we're going to look at the hot spots."},{"time":592000,"text":"Can you tell what's happening\nin a conversation?"},{"time":594310,"text":"Can you start to find the hot spots"},{"time":597000,"text":"to see the discrepancies"},{"time":599000,"text":"between someone's words\nand someone's actions?"},{"time":601215,"text":"Now, I know it seems really obvious,"},{"time":603000,"text":"but when you're having a conversation\nwith someone you suspect of deception,"},{"time":608000,"text":"attitude is by far the most overlooked\nbut telling of indicators."}]},{"cues":[{"time":611100,"text":"An honest person\nis going to be cooperative."},{"time":613320,"text":"They're going to show\nthey're on your side."},{"time":615392,"text":"They're going to be enthusiastic."},{"time":617000,"text":"They're going to be willing and helpful\nto getting you to the truth."},{"time":620300,"text":"They're going to be willing\nto brainstorm, name suspects,"},{"time":623100,"text":"provide details."},{"time":624400,"text":"They're going to say,"},{"time":626000,"text":"\"Hey, maybe it was those guys in payroll\nthat forged those checks.\""},{"time":629200,"text":"They're going to be infuriated\nif they sense they're wrongly accused"},{"time":632500,"text":"throughout the entire course\nof the interview, not just in flashes;"},{"time":635700,"text":"they'll be infuriated throughout\nthe entire course of the interview."},{"time":638963,"text":"And if you ask someone honest"},{"time":640400,"text":"what should happen\nto whomever did forge those checks,"},{"time":643000,"text":"an honest person is much more likely"},{"time":644800,"text":"to recommend strict rather\nthan lenient punishment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":648000,"text":"Now let's say you're having\nthat exact same conversation"},{"time":650691,"text":"with someone deceptive."},{"time":652000,"text":"That person may be withdrawn,"},{"time":654000,"text":"look down, lower their voice,"},{"time":656000,"text":"pause, be kind of herky-jerky."},{"time":658000,"text":"Ask a deceptive person\nto tell their story,"},{"time":660072,"text":"they're going to pepper it\nwith way too much detail"},{"time":663000,"text":"in all kinds of irrelevant places."},{"time":666000,"text":"And then they're going to tell their story\nin strict chronological order."},{"time":669500,"text":"And what a trained interrogator does"},{"time":671300,"text":"is they come in and in very subtle ways\nover the course of several hours,"},{"time":675000,"text":"they will ask that person\nto tell that story backwards,"},{"time":678000,"text":"and then they'll watch them squirm,"},{"time":680000,"text":"and track which questions produce\nthe highest volume of deceptive tells."}]},{"cues":[{"time":683453,"text":"Why do they do that?\nWell, we all do the same thing."},{"time":686000,"text":"We rehearse our words,"},{"time":688000,"text":"but we rarely rehearse our gestures."},{"time":690000,"text":"We say \"yes,\" we shake our heads \"no.\""},{"time":692000,"text":"We tell very convincing stories,\nwe slightly shrug our shoulders."},{"time":695120,"text":"We commit terrible crimes,"},{"time":697000,"text":"and we smile at the delight\nin getting away with it."},{"time":700000,"text":"Now, that smile is known\nin the trade as \"duping delight.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":703000,"text":"And we're going to see that\nin several videos moving forward,"},{"time":706000,"text":"but we're going to start --\nfor those of you who don't know him,"},{"time":709100,"text":"this is presidential\ncandidate John Edwards"},{"time":711200,"text":"who shocked America by fathering\na child out of wedlock."},{"time":714000,"text":"We're going to see him talk\nabout getting a paternity test."},{"time":717000,"text":"See now if you can spot him\nsaying, \"yes\" while shaking his head \"no,\""},{"time":721024,"text":"slightly shrugging his shoulders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":723000,"text":"(Video) John Edwards: I'd be happy\nto participate in one."},{"time":725700,"text":"I know that it's not possible\nthat this child could be mine,"},{"time":728600,"text":"because of the timing of events."},{"time":730200,"text":"So I know it's not possible."},{"time":732000,"text":"Happy to take a paternity test,\nand would love to see it happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736000,"text":"Interviewer: Are you going to do\nthat soon? Is there somebody --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":739072,"text":"JE: Well, I'm only one side.\nI'm only one side of the test."},{"time":742000,"text":"But I'm happy to participate in one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":745795,"text":"PM: Okay, those head shakes\nare much easier to spot"},{"time":748253,"text":"once you know to look for them."},{"time":749800,"text":"There are going to be times\nwhen someone makes one expression"},{"time":753800,"text":"while masking another that just\nkind of leaks through in a flash."},{"time":757000,"text":"Murderers are known to leak sadness."},{"time":759000,"text":"Your new joint venture partner\nmight shake your hand,"},{"time":761600,"text":"celebrate, go out to dinner with you\nand then leak an expression of anger."},{"time":766000,"text":"And we're not all going to become\nfacial expression experts overnight here,"},{"time":769600,"text":"but there's one I can teach you\nthat's very dangerous"},{"time":772102,"text":"and it's easy to learn,"},{"time":773339,"text":"and that's the expression of contempt."},{"time":775200,"text":"Now with anger, you've got\ntwo people on an even playing field."},{"time":778224,"text":"It's still somewhat\nof a healthy relationship."},{"time":780439,"text":"But when anger turns to contempt,\nyou've been dismissed."},{"time":784000,"text":"It's associated with moral superiority."},{"time":786000,"text":"And for that reason, it's very,\nvery hard to recover from."},{"time":789000,"text":"Here's what it looks like."},{"time":791000,"text":"It's marked by one lip corner\npulled up and in."},{"time":795000,"text":"It's the only asymmetrical expression."},{"time":798000,"text":"And in the presence of contempt,\nwhether or not deception follows --"},{"time":802000,"text":"and it doesn't always follow --"},{"time":804000,"text":"look the other way,\ngo the other direction,"},{"time":806072,"text":"reconsider the deal,"},{"time":808000,"text":"say, \"No thank you. I'm not coming up\nfor just one more nightcap. Thank you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":812000,"text":"Science has surfaced\nmany, many more indicators."},{"time":816000,"text":"We know, for example,"},{"time":818000,"text":"we know liars will shift their blink rate,"},{"time":820024,"text":"point their feet towards an exit."},{"time":822000,"text":"They will take barrier objects"},{"time":824000,"text":"and put them between themselves\nand the person that is interviewing them."},{"time":827453,"text":"They'll alter their vocal tone,"},{"time":829000,"text":"often making their vocal tone much lower."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832000,"text":"Now here's the deal."},{"time":834000,"text":"These behaviors are just behaviors."},{"time":837000,"text":"They're not proof of deception."},{"time":839000,"text":"They're red flags."},{"time":841000,"text":"We're human beings."},{"time":843000,"text":"We make deceptive flailing gestures\nall over the place all day long."},{"time":846300,"text":"They don't mean anything\nin and of themselves."},{"time":848515,"text":"But when you see clusters\nof them, that's your signal."},{"time":851100,"text":"Look, listen, probe,\nask some hard questions,"},{"time":854000,"text":"get out of that very comfortable\nmode of knowing,"},{"time":857000,"text":"walk into curiosity mode,\nask more questions,"},{"time":860000,"text":"have a little dignity, treat the person\nyou're talking to with rapport."},{"time":863400,"text":"Don't try to be like those folks\non \"Law &amp; Order\" and those other TV shows"},{"time":867000,"text":"that pummel their subjects\ninto submission."},{"time":869072,"text":"Don't be too aggressive, it doesn't work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":872119,"text":"Now, we've talked a little bit\nabout how to talk to someone who's lying"},{"time":875500,"text":"and how to spot a lie."},{"time":877000,"text":"And as I promised, we're now going\nto look at what the truth looks like."},{"time":880500,"text":"But I'm going to show you two videos,"},{"time":882300,"text":"two mothers -- one is lying,\none is telling the truth."},{"time":885000,"text":"And these were surfaced by researcher\nDavid Matsumoto in California."},{"time":889120,"text":"And I think they're an excellent example\nof what the truth looks like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":893000,"text":"This mother, Diane Downs,"},{"time":895000,"text":"shot her kids at close range,"},{"time":897000,"text":"drove them to the hospital\nwhile they bled all over the car,"},{"time":901000,"text":"claimed a scraggy-haired stranger did it."},{"time":903000,"text":"And you'll see when you see the video,"},{"time":905000,"text":"she can't even pretend\nto be an agonizing mother."},{"time":907358,"text":"What you want to look for here\nis an incredible discrepancy"},{"time":911000,"text":"between horrific events that she describes\nand her very, very cool demeanor."},{"time":915000,"text":"And if you look closely, you'll see\nduping delight throughout this video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":918500,"text":"(Video) Diane Downs:\nAt night when I close my eyes,"},{"time":921000,"text":"I can see Christie reaching\nher hand out to me while I'm driving,"},{"time":924120,"text":"and the blood just kept\ncoming out of her mouth."},{"time":926400,"text":"And that -- maybe\nit'll fade too with time --"},{"time":928567,"text":"but I don't think so."},{"time":930000,"text":"That bothers me the most."}]},{"cues":[{"time":940000,"text":"PM: Now I'm going to show you a video"}]},{"cues":[{"time":942000,"text":"of an actual grieving mother,\nErin Runnion,"},{"time":944072,"text":"confronting her daughter's murderer\nand torturer in court."},{"time":948000,"text":"Here you're going to see no false emotion,"},{"time":950024,"text":"just the authentic expression\nof a mother's agony."}]},{"cues":[{"time":953000,"text":"(Video) Erin Runnion:\nI wrote this statement"},{"time":955115,"text":"on the third anniversary\nof the night you took my baby,"},{"time":957800,"text":"and you hurt her,"},{"time":959100,"text":"and you crushed her,"},{"time":961000,"text":"you terrified her until her heart stopped."},{"time":965000,"text":"And she fought, and I know she fought you."},{"time":968000,"text":"But I know she looked at you\nwith those amazing brown eyes,"},{"time":972000,"text":"and you still wanted to kill her."},{"time":975000,"text":"And I don't understand it,"},{"time":977000,"text":"and I never will."}]},{"cues":[{"time":980650,"text":"PM: Okay, there's no doubting\nthe veracity of those emotions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":984000,"text":"Now the technology\naround what the truth looks like"},{"time":987000,"text":"is progressing on, the science of it."},{"time":990000,"text":"We know, for example,"},{"time":992000,"text":"that we now have specialized eye trackers\nand infrared brain scans,"},{"time":995167,"text":"MRI's that can decode the signals\nthat our bodies send out"},{"time":998000,"text":"when we're trying to be deceptive."},{"time":1000000,"text":"And these technologies are going\nto be marketed to all of us"},{"time":1003000,"text":"as panaceas for deceit,"},{"time":1005000,"text":"and they will prove\nincredibly useful some day."},{"time":1008000,"text":"But you've got to ask yourself\nin the meantime:"},{"time":1010263,"text":"Who do you want on your side\nof the meeting,"},{"time":1012383,"text":"someone who's trained\nin getting to the truth"},{"time":1015000,"text":"or some guy who's going to drag\na 400-pound electroencephalogram"},{"time":1018100,"text":"through the door?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1019400,"text":"Liespotters rely on human tools."},{"time":1023000,"text":"They know, as someone once said,"},{"time":1025000,"text":"\"Character's who you are in the dark.\""},{"time":1027000,"text":"And what's kind of interesting\nis that today, we have so little darkness."},{"time":1031000,"text":"Our world is lit up 24 hours a day."},{"time":1034000,"text":"It's transparent\nwith blogs and social networks"},{"time":1038000,"text":"broadcasting the buzz\nof a whole new generation of people"},{"time":1040700,"text":"that have made a choice to live\ntheir lives in public."},{"time":1043300,"text":"It's a much more noisy world."},{"time":1047000,"text":"So one challenge we have is to remember,"},{"time":1051000,"text":"oversharing, that's not honesty."},{"time":1054000,"text":"Our manic tweeting and texting\ncan blind us"},{"time":1058000,"text":"to the fact that the subtleties\nof human decency -- character integrity --"},{"time":1061600,"text":"that's still what matters,\nthat's always what's going to matter."},{"time":1064672,"text":"So in this much noisier world,"},{"time":1066200,"text":"it might make sense for us"},{"time":1068000,"text":"to be just a little bit more explicit\nabout our moral code."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1073000,"text":"When you combine the science\nof recognizing deception"},{"time":1075600,"text":"with the art of looking, listening,"},{"time":1077300,"text":"you exempt yourself\nfrom collaborating in a lie."},{"time":1080000,"text":"You start up that path\nof being just a little bit more explicit,"},{"time":1084000,"text":"because you signal to everyone around you,"},{"time":1086024,"text":"you say, \"Hey, my world, our world,\nit's going to be an honest one."},{"time":1091000,"text":"My world is going to be\none where truth is strengthened"},{"time":1093644,"text":"and falsehood is recognized\nand marginalized.\""},{"time":1096000,"text":"And when you do that,"},{"time":1098000,"text":"the ground around you starts\nto shift just a little bit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1101000,"text":"And that's the truth. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1104000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}